## ✨ Features

### 👨‍🎓 Student Features
- Register/Login with JWT authentication
- View assigned room details
- Submit complaints (electricity, water, etc.)
- Apply for leave requests
- Track complaint & leave status

### 🧑‍💼 Admin Features
- Dashboard with live stats
- Room management (create/update/assign students)
- Complaint management (resolve/reject/in-progress)
- Leave approval/rejection system
- View all students and rooms

## 🛠 Tech Stack

Frontend:
- React.js
- Tailwind CSS
- Axios

Backend:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT Authentication

Other:
- Cloudinary (image upload)